# 8. Heapify Algorithm

Most Important Function.

### Goal

Make subtree rooted at index i satisfy Max Heap property.

---

### Algorithm

```text
heapify(arr, n, i)

largest = i

left = 2*i + 1

right = 2*i + 2

If left child > largest
    largest = left

If right child > largest
    largest = right

If largest != i

    swap

    heapify(largest)
```

