# 21. Common Mistakes

## Mistake 1

Wrong Child Formula

Wrong:

```java
left = 2*i;
right = 2*i+1;
```

Correct:

```java
left = 2*i+1;
right = 2*i+2;
```

---

## Mistake 2

Building Heap from Start

Wrong:

```java
for(i=0;i<n;i++)
```

Correct:

```java
for(i=n/2-1;i>=0;i--)
```

---

## Mistake 3

Forgetting Reduced Heap Size

Wrong:

```java
heapify(arr, n, 0);
```

Correct:

```java
heapify(arr, i, 0);
```

